We were absolutely honored to welcome the renowned makeup artist Rohini Kakade Ma’am to House of Dechen!

It was a true delight to have her experience our craftsmanship firsthand and speak so warmly about our work.

At House of Dechen, we specialize in designing and customizing entire wedding trousseaus — for Women, Men, and Kids. From bridal wear to attire for all functions for the entire family, every piece is crafted with love and detail.

Visit us in Camp, Pune to explore our bespoke collection www.houseofdechen.in

latestPosts.caption:
At House of Dechen, we always felt that there was something missing in men’s wear, be it shirts or traditional kurtas.

Something that felt rooted in heritage —

but powerful in silence.

Something that didn’t scream gold,

but carried it like a legacy.

Welcome to EDEN OF GOLD —

crafted for the modern man, grounded in timeless power.

Stay tuned to know more about our new collection. ✨

#HouseofDechen #luxurycomfort #handcrafted #sustainableluxury #inclusivefashion #handcraftedoutfits #sustainableclothing #ethnicmenswear #ethnicmenswearcollection

Inspired by nature’s rich texture and gold’s enduring warmth, every piece from the Eden of Gold collection is crafted to reflect character and prestige, without needing to be overt.

This is more than just clothing.

It is identity.

It is pride in who you are and where you come from.

It is grace in strength, and depth in detail.

Stay tuned to know more about the collection.
